content:
Certainly! Below is an example of HTML code for a landing page designed as per your requirements:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Smartphone Launch</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            background-color: #ff5733;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .tshirt-design {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .tshirt-design img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        .features, .reviews {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .features h2, .reviews h2 {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .reviews blockquote {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-left: 5px solid #007bff;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Introducing the All-New Smartphone</h1>
        <a href="#learn-more" class="cta-button">Learn More</a>
    </header>

    <div class="tshirt-design">
        <h2>Our Unique T-Shirt Design</h2>
        <img src="smartphone-tshirt.jpg" alt="T-Shirt Design with Smartphone">
        <p><strong>"Revolutionize Your World"</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Stunning camera quality for perfect shots</li>
            <li>Long-lasting battery life to keep you going</li>
            <li>Massive storage capacity for all your needs</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="reviews">
        <h2>Customer Reviews</h2>
        <blockquote>
            <p>"The best smartphone I've ever used!" - Jane Doe</p>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote>
            <p>"Incredible battery life and camera quality." - John Smith</p>
        </blockquote>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

### Explanation:
- **Header**: Contains the product name and a call-to-action button to learn more.
- **T-Shirt Design Section**: Displays an image (a placeholder here, replace with actual image source) and a catchy slogan.
- **Features Section**: Lists key features of the smartphone.
- **Reviews Section**: Includes customer reviews and testimonials.

Feel free to customize the content and styles to match your brand's identity or to include more specific details about your smartphone.
